-- Pacific Plywood to Purchase 51% of Hong Kong Moneylender for HK$52 Million
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-09-24T15:09:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-24/pacific-plywood-to-purchase-51-of-hong-kong-moneylender-for-hk-52-million.html
Pacific Plywood Holdings Ltd.  will
pay HK$52 million in cash, new shares and convertible notes for
a 51 percent stake in Hong Kong moneylender Head & Shoulders
Finance Ltd., the company said in a Hong Kong stock exchange
announcement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  